

=Description=

"Occupy & Demand is built in solidarity with Occupy Wall Street and Occupy Together. It is a platform designed to centralize the demands of the national Occupy activist movement. The platform allows users to make demands and vote on those made by others.

We hope this tool will be used to better reflect the collective will of Occupy activists around the country, and that people will use this platform to articulate their demands."
(http://www.occupyanddemand.org/)


